### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Get JWT Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/token/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "root",
    "password": "root"
}

### Verify JWT Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/token/verify/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "token": "{{token}}"
}

### STOCKS ###

### Get All Tickers
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/reference/tickers
    ?market=stocks
    &active=true
    &order=asc
    &limit=100
    &sort=ticker
#Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Single Ticker Details (AAPL)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/reference/tickers/AAPL
#Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Related Tickers (AAPL)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/related-companies/AAPL
#Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Stock Aggregates (Daily for AAPL)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/aggs/ticker/AAPL/range/1/day/2023-01-09/2023-02-10
    ?adjusted=true
    &sort=asc
    &limit=120
#Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Previous Day Bar (AAPL)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/aggs/ticker/AAPL/prev
    ?adjusted=true
#Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Single Stock Snapshot (AAPL)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/snapshot/stocks/tickers/AAPL
#Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Full Market Snapshot
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/snapshot/stocks/tickers
#Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Unified Snapshot
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/snapshot
    ?order=asc
    &limit=10
    &sort=ticker
#Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Market Gainers
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/snapshot/stocks/gainers
#Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Stock Trades
