### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Notes:
# 1. Replace 'your_jwt_token_here' with an actual token from /api/token/ endpoint
# 2. All endpoints require JWT authentication except in local environment
# 3. The proxy preserves Polygon.io's original response structure
# 4. Query parameters are passed through to Polygon.io API
# 5. Our API uses /v1/ prefix which maps to appropriate Polygon.io API versions internally
# 6. Version mapping:
#    - Most endpoints use v3
#    - Aggregates (aggs) use v2
#    - Some legacy endpoints use v1 (open-close, meta/symbols, etc.) 